title: Romelo Banks Out 6 Weeks Following Ankle Surgery
text: Romelo Banks Out 6 Weeks Following Ankle Surgery JACKSONVILLE -- North Florida junior center underwent a surgical procedure on his ankle and is expected to return to the Osprey lineup in six weeks."We hate for any of our guys to have to face injuries," said head coach Matthew Driscoll . "However, we are looking forward to having a fully healthy Romelo back in six weeks ready to contribute to our team the way someone with his size and skill set can do."UNF, in the midst of preseason practices, opens the 2015-16 season Nov. 13 on the road at Illinois before hosting UT Rio Grande Valley, Nov. 16, at 7 p.m. in UNF Arena for their home debut.
